Package: oncoscanR
Type: Package
Title: Meta-analyses of CNV segments
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person("Yann", "Christinat", email = "yann.christinat@hcuge.ch", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Taking copy number segments as input (either ChAS export file or ChAS-like text file), 
    identify chromosome arms that are globally altered and computes various scores.
